         <abstract id="aspace_82a89113f645a8dfbbca69559f3f4015">The papers are largely letters from Charlotte Coffyn Wilkinson Bradgon, Class of 1884, to Charlotte May Wilkinson, her mother, with additional letters containing information on her life.</abstract>
